{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_15","type":"agent_message","text":"The failure is not a clean `Missing*RegistrationError`; the image builds, then runtime falls over inside Netty’s adaptive allocator with a `NullPointerException` during `ReferenceCountUpdater.setInitialValue`, which strongly suggests the new `5.0.1` metadata is incomplete or conditioned too narrowly rather than the test fixture itself being wrong."}}
